<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<table border="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td width="42%"><a href="categories/music.asp"><img border="0" src="crazy/matthew1.jpg"></a></td>
    <td width="58%">
      <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="2">When children laugh and dance
      and sing,<br>
      And monkeys wear their wedding rings,<br>
      I shall puke and scream and shout,<br>
      &quot;Lookie, fat mommy, I've started to pout!&quot;</font></p>
      <p align="left"><font face="Arial" size="2">For thy undies, in a wad, they
      have become<br>
      And thy toothache, it pulsates betwixt thy gums,<br>
      Whilst women quake upon my mean machine<br>
      I am fire, I am water -- I <i>am</i> Steve McQueen.<br>
      <br>
      -- Tonto, <i>The Last Of The Gay Slimpies</i></font></td>
  </tr>
</table>
